{
    "typeName": "TF::VSphere::VmStoragePolicy",
    "description": "The `vsphere_vm_storage_policy` resource can be used to create and manage storage \npolicies. Using this storage policy, tag based placement rules can be created to \nplace a VM on a particular tagged datastore.",
